name: A Hope
description:
Bismillahi, tawakkaltu 'alallah, laa haula wa laa quwwata illaa billaah

Dengan nama Allah, aku bertawakal kepada Allah. Tiada daya dan kekuatan kecuali dengan Allah

In the name of Allah, I put my trust in Allah. There is no power and strength except with Allah

This works dedicated to the community.
Thank you for fellow artists and collectors who always give full of support. Cheers~
